title: Is unsqueeze supported for ONNX (looks like yes, but doc doesn't say it)
body_html: Looks like PyTorch ONNX support does include unsqueeze operator. However doc here doesn't mention it. I'm wondering if doc just need to be updated or if there is something else missing to support unsqueeze operator.

body: Looks like PyTorch ONNX support [does include](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/torch/onnx/symbolic.py#L738) `unsqueeze` operator. However [doc here](https://pytorch.org/docs/stable/onnx.html#supported-operators) doesn't mention it. I'm wondering if doc just need to be updated or if there is something else missing to support `unsqueeze` operator.
